OL,3,C'Single biggest issue': Judge on
OL,4,Cviolence against women and girls
OL,6,FA top judge says the level of violence
OL,7,Fagainst women and girls is at a
OL,8,F'chronic' level and the single biggest
OL,9,Fissue facing Northern Ireland society
OL,10,Fand the criminal justice system.
OL,12,FJudge Steven Keown said it was a
OL,13,Fproblem he sees every day in his
OL,14,Fcourts describing it as "depressing".
OL,15,FHe said new laws protecting victims
OL,16,Fand changes in how domestic abuse
OL,17,Fcases are handled are making a
OL,18,Fdifference.
